msgctxt "Talk_000"
msgid ""
"<1.so>They say it's too dangerous to go\n"
"outside of the village right now.\n"
"\n"
"But all I want to do is go sing with my\n"
"sisters at <2.se_co>Warbler's Nest<3.re_co>...\n"
"\n"
"<4.so><5.te_si>That <6.se_co>Divine Beast Vah Medoh <7.re_co>is\n"
"a big jerk!<8.te_si>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: animation
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk_001"
msgid "<1.so><2.an>Kheel! <3.pa>Watch your language!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_002"
msgid "<1.so>But, but..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: set_colour (red)
#. 5: reset_colour
msgctxt "Talk_003"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Could you...maybe tell that <2.se_co>Medoh<3.re_co> thing\n"
"to go somewhere else? I want to go\n"
"practice my singing at <4.se_co>Warbler's Nest<5.re_co>."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (red)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "Talk_010"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm headed to <2.se_co>Warbler's Nest<3.re_co>!\n"
"I hope it's safe there."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "Talk_020"
msgid ""
"<1.so><2.se_co>Medoh <3.re_co>was up there all day today.\n"
"I wish it would go away..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
msgctxt "Talk_030"
msgid "<1.so>*sniff*"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "Talk_100"
msgid ""
"<1.so>When I told the <2.se_co>village elder<3.re_co> that this\n"
"shrine popped out of the ground, he was\n"
"so surprised!\n"
"I guess shrines like playing hide-and-\n"
"seek too!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: pause (short)
#. 4: pause (short)
#. 5: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk_101"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Poppy used to sing about shrines\n"
"in his songs.\n"
"\n"
"<2.so>But...<3.pa>he never comes home anymore...<4.pa>\n"
"I miss...<5.pa>his voice."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_110"
msgid ""
"<1.so>We're all going to go sing.\n"
"You should come listen to us!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_120"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I've been getting better and better at\n"
"singing! Gonna do my best tomorrow\n"
"too!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: text_size
#. 3: text_size
msgctxt "Talk_200"
msgid ""
"<1.so>♪<2.te_si>La la laaaa!♪<3.te_si>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Poppy's back! We're all gonna sing\n"
"together!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_201"
msgid ""
"<1.so>We're all gonna sing with Poppy!\n"
"Come listen to us!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_202"
msgid "<1.so>It's so fun singing with everyone!"
msgstr ""

